{
  "texts": [
    "The model is evaluated on 100 validation sets from DIV2K.",
    "During training and testing, each image in the dataset is cropped to 128×128 to obtain the HR image.",
    "The HR image is then downsampled using a bi-cubic kernel to generate an LR image of size 32×32.",
    "Additionally, for the general-purpose SISR task (2×), we utilized the CIFAR-10 dataset, which comprises 60,000 images across ten categories.",
    "During training and testing, each image in the dataset (32×32) was downsampled using bicubic interpolation to (16×16) resolution."
  ]
}